<p><strong>DRX 21.00</strong></p>
<p><strong>FNC 31.00</strong></p>
<p><strong>LGD 36.00</strong></p>
<p><strong>MAD 71.00</strong></p>
<p><strong>TSM 81.00</strong></p>
<p><strong>TL 81.00</strong></p>
